{"tid":2205423,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"尼泊爾斥資7000萬美元 為EBC提供免費WiFi","createTime":"2020-09-16T21:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T11:04:26.000Z","uid":265932,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c05cce5bc6efd04fd2317be8d286436568db8d","tid":2205423,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T21:32:14.000Z","msg":"山區網絡全面提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尼泊爾電訊管理局 NTA 宣佈，政府將斥資6900萬美元，於各個山區興建無線網絡發射站，除咗 EBC 珠峰大本營外，亦包括 Lobuche，Monjo，Namche Bazaar，Phakding，Feriche 和 Tengboche 等山區，預計8個月之後可以提供免費 WiFi 服務。而有關承建商聲稱已解決地勢及高海拔問題，於零下20度之下，仍可提供高速 WiFi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://fitz.hk/?p=140383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffitz.hk%2F%3Fp%3D140383&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=f469a0eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://fitz.hk/?p=140383</a>"},{"pid":"b9b3a79f846eae89bd54218dacfb64ca9232828c","tid":2205423,"uid":312205,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T22:16:18.000Z","msg":"本身都唔多人去"},{"pid":"49e0f09c460a5c53988a0c0394eb16b15d0822a2","tid":2205423,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T23:25:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1cc26d76da515889af52cfdd1477c69aac4bd5c","tid":2205423,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T23:29:27.000Z","msg":"6年前行abc已經周圍WiFi"},{"pid":"0897f5c4ac25a3710ad47454c7c28acbbc2d1839","tid":2205423,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1cc26d76da515889af52cfdd1477c69aac4bd5c","tid":2205423,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T23:29:27.000Z","msg":"6年前行abc已經周圍WiFi"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"可唔可以睇youtube"},{"pid":"e9bd8620f8ea8942a35bac2ca5d6caa0e90d4959","tid":2205423,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b3a79f846eae89bd54218d